    <note>Zhao(1) Shanjian [7179] Rue's [7178] father, Zhang(1) Shuye's [8018] grandson-in-law. He was Liangzhe yunfu in 1199, became prefect of Linan fu in 1200, Gongbu shilang in 1201, Hubu shilang in 1205, and Hubu shangshu in 1208. Jiangxi TZ, 22.19b; SS(PRC), 230.7330; Author Unknown, Qingyuan dang jin (ZBZZ ed.); Xianchun Linan zhi, 50.9a; SHY:ZG, 73.30b, 35a, 40a. CBD, 5, 3576-7.From Hartwell's ACTIVITY table:1199:  Apt. Liangzhe yunfu1200:  From Liangzhe yunfu apt. prefect of Linan fu1201:  From provisional Gongbu shiliang concurrently prefect of Linan fu, apt. to a temple sinecure125:  from provisional Hubu shilang, apt. to a temple sinecure1208:  Dismissed (fangba) as Hubu shangshu</note>
